OL,3,CMinister writes to councils after ITV
OL,4,CNews reveals children sleeping rough
OL,6,FThe UK government's minister for
OL,7,Fhomelessness has written to local
OL,8,Fcouncils in England after ITV News
OL,9,Frevealed that children as young as
OL,10,Ffour had been left to sleep on the
OL,11,Fstreets.
OL,13,FAlison McGovern MP has sent the
OL,14,Fwarning to leaders and chief
OL,15,Fexecutives, expressing her concern
OL,16,Fafter seeing the report, telling them
OL,17,Fthat "legislation is clear that a
OL,18,Fchild should never sleep on the
OL,19,Fstreets."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
