OL,3,CMinister writes to councils after ITV
OL,4,CNews reveals children sleeping rough
OL,6,FAlison McGovern MP told ITV News: "If
OL,7,Fwe are at the stage where we've got
OL,8,Fchildren at risk of being on the
OL,9,Fstreets, that is an abysmal state of
OL,10,Faffairs"
OL,12,FHer comments come after ITV News
OL,13,Frevealed that young families are
OL,14,Fsleeping rough, with local councils in
OL,15,FEngland being accused of breaking the
OL,16,Flaw by denying them emergency
OL,17,Faccommodation.
OL,26,@nD@cOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
