OL,3,CMinister writes to councils after ITV
OL,4,CNews reveals children sleeping rough
OL,6,FWe spoke to one homeless family in
OL,7,FLondon with five children who slept on
OL,8,Fthe streets for almost two weeks in
OL,9,FDecember, and another family with
OL,10,Fthree children in Birmingham, all
OL,11,Funder the age of 12, who were forced
OL,12,Fto sleep in their car.
OL,14,FBoth families were turned away by
OL,15,Flocal councils, which refused to
OL,16,Fprovide the accommodation after they
OL,17,Fbecame homeless.
OL,19,FRead the full responses to ITV News
OL,20,Ffrom the relevant councils here.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
