OL,3,CMinister writes to councils after ITV
OL,4,CNews reveals children sleeping rough
OL,6,FThe charity Crisis said councils are
OL,7,Fincreasingly "competing with each
OL,8,Fother to not help children who are
OL,9,Fsleeping rough, which is something we
OL,10,Fhave never seen.
OL,12,FThe charity told ITV News their
OL,13,Frecords show 100 homeless families
OL,14,Fwith children, pregnant mothers, have
OL,15,Fcome to them for help after being
OL,16,Fturned away by local authorities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
