OL,3,CMinister writes to councils after ITV
OL,4,CNews reveals children sleeping rough
OL,6,FLatest government figures, a snapshot
OL,7,Ftaken on a single night in Autumn
OL,8,F2024, show there was a year-on-year
OL,9,Fincrease of 20% in the number of
OL,10,Fpeople sleeping rough in England
OL,11,F(3,898 in 2023 up to 4,667 in 2024).
OL,13,FIf you or your family have been
OL,14,Faffected by this story, you can
OL,15,Fcontact us at investigations@itv.com
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
