OL,3,CMinister writes to councils after ITV
OL,4,CNews reveals children sleeping rough
OL,6,FIn her letter, McGovern reminded
OL,7,Fcouncils of their legal obligations,
OL,8,Fwriting: "The welfare of children is
OL,9,Fparamount. Safeguarding and promoting
OL,10,Fthe welfare of children is everyone's
OL,11,Fresponsibility, and it is a priority
OL,12,Ffor this Government.
OL,14,F"I am therefore extremely concerned
OL,15,Fabout the recent reports of families
OL,16,Fwith children sleeping rough, whilst
OL,17,Flocal authorities determine which
OL,18,Fcouncil is responsible for housing
OL,19,Fthem. This should never happen.
OL,26,@pD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
