OL,3,CMinister writes to councils after ITV
OL,4,CNews reveals children sleeping rough
OL,6,F"The relevant legislation is clear
OL,7,Fthat a child should never be sleeping
OL,8,Fon the streets, in cars or any other
OL,9,Fplace not designed for living in. A
OL,10,Fhousehold with a child has priority
OL,11,Fneed for the purposes of the Housing
OL,12,FAct 1996.
OL,14,F"Eligible homeless households with
OL,15,Fchildren must be accommodated under
OL,16,Fsection 188, and in some circumstances
OL,17,Funder section 190(2) or 193 of the Act.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
