OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772132672
OL,3,CMinister writes to councils after ITV
OL,4,CNews reveals children sleeping rough
OL,6,F"During the period where an authority
OL,7,Fis determining which legal duty
OL,8,Fapplies, and which council owes those
OL,9,Fduties, it is never acceptable to
OL,10,Fallow a child to sleep on the streets.
OL,12,F"Where households do not meet the
OL,13,Fcriteria for homelessness assistance,
OL,14,Flocal authorities have a duty under
OL,15,Fsection 17 of the Children Act 1989 to
OL,16,Fsafeguard and promote the welfare of
OL,17,Fchildren who are in need, including
OL,18,Fproviding them with accommodation
OL,19,Fwhere necessary.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
